{"tid":1069382,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"如果辦一間唔收支那學生嘅中/小學有冇得諗?","createTime":"2019-03-20T02:46:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-20T04:08:02.000Z","uid":120814,"like":7,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"13e46a1f715402dd15ec26198d3aaf3f33fed237","tid":1069382,"uid":120814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:46:00.000Z","msg":"分上/下晝兩班<br />\n只收雙親都係香港人/非中國藉嘅學生<br />\n控制南亞學生數量, 每班不多於一個<br />\n<br />\n必修: <br />\n英文 <br />\n一個以上歐洲語言/日文<br />\n哲學/宗教<br />\n音樂藝術<br />\n創意科學<br />\n體育<br />\n性教育<br />\n<br />\n無功課 / 無考試 <br />\n無校服 / 無髮禁<br />\n唯一會罰就係講支那語同寫殘體字<br />\n<br />\n日校模式, 無校舍可能好似補習學校搵商業大廈開班 / 走出課室戶外活動<br />\n救國之餘又可以撈返筆, 有冇得諗下?"},{"pid":"fde8d03c9520ae9a7dd00d0b82f02e47fd8b687d","tid":1069382,"uid":204227,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"如果係中學嘅點考dse，強制要學生考IB?"},{"pid":"46b3724835c91184931709f12c942e40f10efa26","tid":1069382,"uid":60279,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:47:13.000Z","msg":"你點過到EDB果關?<br />\n無考試又點會有父母理你"},{"pid":"98014e0efd4f7633f7f8a585ceb011b030397f62","tid":1069382,"uid":16061,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:47:50.000Z","msg":"同港獨一樣 得個諗字<br />\n完全無可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3a70224196d38ae54af68b3c97b45de0601d340","tid":1069382,"uid":196924,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:49:24.000Z","msg":"我淨係知道你會成為連登第一才子(坐緊監)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"115be42aab755ebc3060c662d06ccd7ce1312086","tid":1069382,"uid":200521,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:54:33.000Z","msg":"講獨鍵國啲fd？"},{"pid":"9b45e04816ac6cba6b06a3bb58ec3dfb88ed91ae","tid":1069382,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-20T02:55:55.000Z","msg":"你拎到牌先算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid